```plaintext
Subject: Last Chance: Exclusive Savings on Your Favorite Products!

Dear [Recipient's Name],

We’re excited to offer you an exclusive deal that’s only available for a limited time. This offer is valid until [specific date] because we’re discontinuing the product soon.

Meet Sarah, who saved $500 on her home renovation by following our tips. Could you do the same?

Here’s what you’ll get:
- 20% Off Your First Purchase
- Free Shipping on Orders Over $50
- Exclusive Access to New Products

Don’t miss out—this offer ends tomorrow!

[Visual: Image of a before-and-after home renovation]

Act Fast: This Offer Ends Tomorrow!

[CTA Button: Shop Now]

Best regards,
[Your Name]
[Your Company]

P.S.: Stay updated on our latest offers by following us on [social media handles].
```

To make this more visually appealing and professional, you can format it as follows:

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1, h2 {
            color: #333333;
        }
        p {
            color: #555555;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007BFF;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
        .image-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .image-container img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }
        .p-s {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Last Chance: Exclusive Savings on Your Favorite Products!</h1>
        <p>Dear [Recipient's Name],</p>

        <p>We’re excited to offer you an exclusive deal that’s only available for a limited time. This offer is valid until [specific date] because we’re discontinuing the product soon.</p>

        <p>Meet Sarah, who saved $500 on her home renovation by following our tips. Could you do the same?</p>

        <ul>
            <li>20% Off Your First Purchase</li>
            <li>Free Shipping on Orders Over $50</li>
            <li>Exclusive Access to New Products</li>
        </ul>

        <p><strong>Don’t miss out—this offer ends tomorrow!</strong></p>

        <div class="image-container">
            <img src="https://example.com/before-after-renovation.jpg" alt="Before and After Home Renovation">
        </div>

        <a href="[your-website-url]" class="cta-button">Shop Now</a>

        <p class="p-s">Best regards,<br>[Your Name]<br>[Your Company]</p>

        <p class="p-s">P.S.: Stay updated on our latest offers by following us on <a href="[social-media-url]">@YourCompany</a>.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
```

### Explanation:
1. **HTML Structure**: The HTML structure includes a container for the main content, headers, paragraphs, and a call-to-action button.
2. **CSS Styling**: Basic CSS is included to style the email, ensuring it looks professional and is responsive.
3. **Visual Elements**: An image is included to make the email more engaging.
4. **CTA Button**: A styled button is provided to make the call-to-action clear and prominent.
5. **Personalization**: Placeholder text like `[Recipient's Name]`, `[specific date]`, `[your-website-url]`, and `[social-media-url]` are included for customization.

This formatted email should look professional and be effective in motivating action while maintaining ethical standards.

